    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_commonskill",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "さあ、お掃除を始めましょう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_commonskill.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_1_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "こうして先生と時間を過ごせること……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_1_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "私は、それが本当に嬉しいのです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_2_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "お腹が空いたら仰ってくださいね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_2_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "「メイド」の私であれば手料理をご用意するところですが……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_2_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今は、「生徒」ですから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_2_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_3_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "お呼びでしょうか、先生？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_3_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "呼んだだけ、ですか……？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_3_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "うふふっ、あらあら。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_3_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_4_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ふふっ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlobby_4_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生は……どうなのか教えていただけますか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlogin_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "お待ちしておりました、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlogin_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlogin_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "行きたい場所があれば、遠慮なく仰ってくださいね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlogin_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlogin_season_1_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "普段から賑やかですが、今日のミレニアムは一入ですね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlogin_season_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlogin_season_1_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "活気があるのは、良いことですが。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlogin_season_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlogin_season_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "いよいよ大詰めですね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlogin_season_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlogin_season_end_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ミレニアムEXPO、お楽しみいただけましたか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlogin_season_end_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_eventlogin_season_end_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "私は先生とご一緒できて光栄でした。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_eventlogin_season_end_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_exskill_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "あら、こんにちは？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_exskill_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_exskill_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "こちらにいらっしゃったのですね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_exskill_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_exskill_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "伏せていてくださいね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_exskill_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_exskill_level_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "では、仕上げといきましょう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_exskill_level_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_exskill_level_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "本日のお仕事は、こちらで終わり。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_exskill_level_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_exskill_level_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "綺麗に掃除いたしましょう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_exskill_level_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_exweapon_get",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "キヴォトスにおいて、銃は必需品です。それはメイドだろうと、生徒だろうと変わりません。数多ある銃の中……先生から頂戴したこの「掃除道具」と共に、これからも精進いたしますね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_exweapon_get.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_formation_in_1",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "どちらへ行かれますか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_formation_in_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_formation_in_2",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ミレニアムの日常をごゆっくりお楽しみください。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_formation_in_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_formation_select",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "改まってこうお呼びするのも新鮮ですね。……先生？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_formation_select.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_gachaget",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ミレニアムサイエンススクール、コールサインゼロスリー室笠アカネ。生徒としてご挨拶申し上げます。ふふっ、もともと生徒なのですけどね？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_gachaget.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_growup_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "完璧なメイドとして、文武両道でなければなりません。生徒としても同じく。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_growup_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_growup_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "いつも気にかけてくださりありがとうございます。ご主人様に応えられるよう、尽力いたします。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_growup_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_growup_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "すべては毎日の積み重ね。もしも、その日常を先生が共にしてくださるとしたら……あるいは、異なる未来が待ち受けているのかもしれません。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_growup_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_growup_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "余裕ができてきたので、新しいお掃除の仕方を考えていたんです。最近は撤去用の爆裂カートリッジを研究していまして……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_growup_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生とご主人様、どちらでお呼びしましょう？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "なるほど……先生をご希望ですか。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_1_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "承知しました、「先生」。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_1_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "「生徒」として先生に接する……なんだか不思議な感覚です。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "もちろん、私は普段から先生の生徒ではあるのですが。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "お掃除にも流儀があります。私は少しばかり好みが偏っていますけれど……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ふふっ。どちらの「お掃除」も、ですね。凝り性なんです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ミレニアムの専属教員に、なってくださったりしませんか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "そうすれば毎日先生の授業を受けられますし……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_4_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "「ミレニアムの先生」いい響きだと思うのですが。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_4_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "私は「優等生」と評されることが多いのですが……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_5_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "内面までそうとは限りません。人は誰しも内に秘めたものがありますので。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_5_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_5_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ですから――",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_5_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_lobby_5_4",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生と生徒の火遊びなんて……いかがでしょう？冗談ですよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_lobby_5_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_login_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "おかえりなさい、先生。「授業の準備」は整えております。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_login_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_login_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "本日の「授業」はどの単元でしょうか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_login_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_login_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "メリハリのある指導、よろしくおねがいしますね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_login_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ふふっ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "思っていたより……気恥ずかしいものですね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "自分に対して、素直になる……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "どうにも慣れない感覚です。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ええ、仰る通りです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "私にとって、必要なことだったのだと思います。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生には色々とご迷惑をおかけしてしまいました。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "それでも、先生と出会えた私はやはり――",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_4_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ええ、本当に幸運だったと思っています。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_4_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "すべては流れ、いずれ忘れられていくのでしょう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_5_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今この瞬間でさえ、いつかは……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_5_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_6_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ですが、私は覚えています。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_6_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_6_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "たとえ先生が忘れてしまったとしても。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_6_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_memoriallobby_6_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "本当に大切なものは、決して失われませんから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_memoriallobby_6_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_relationship_up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ときどき、想像してしまうのです。もしも先生と違う出会い方をしていたら、と。例えば……「同級生」だったのなら……。ふふっ、ですが……やはり先生は「先生」なのでしょうね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_relationship_up_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_relationship_up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "制服を着るのは当たり前です。ですが、似合うと言っていただけるのはいつでも嬉しいのですよ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_relationship_up_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_relationship_up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "いつもありがとうございます、先生。そして……そして……。ふぅ、覚悟したつもりでしたが、意外と難しいものですね。いえ、ですから、その……お、お慕い申して……おります……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_relationship_up_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_relationship_up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "放課後、誰も来ない教室があるのですが……お誘いしたら、先生は来てくださるのでしょうか？……ふふっ。冗談です。今は、まだ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_relationship_up_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_birthday_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生、今日が何の日かご存知ですか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_birthday_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_birthday_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "そう、私の誕生日です。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_birthday_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_birthday_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "そして今日は「生徒」として伺いました。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_birthday_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_birthday_4",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "「メイド」では許されずとも、多少はワガママを言っても良いのではないかな、と……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_birthday_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_birthday_5",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ですから、プレゼントとして……先生のお時間が、欲しいです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_birthday_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_birthday_player_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今日は先生のお誕生日ですよね。もちろん覚えています。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_birthday_player_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_birthday_player_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "それで……お祝いは、どちらの私からをご所望ですか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_birthday_player_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_birthday_player_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "生徒？それともメイド？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_birthday_player_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_halloween_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ハロウィーン……お菓子と悪戯があふれる日……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_halloween_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_halloween_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "そこで今日はお菓子を焼いてきました。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_halloween_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_halloween_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "一緒に召し上がってくださいますよね？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_halloween_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_newyear_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "明けましておめでとうございます、先生。本年もよろしくお願いいたします。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_newyear_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_newyear_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今日の私は「メイド」ではありませんので。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_newyear_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_newyear_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "お堅い挨拶は抜きにして……一緒にお参りに行きませんか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_newyear_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_xmas_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "クリスマス、ですね。もしかして……プレゼントを期待しても？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_xmas_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_xmas_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ふふっ、別に用意されていなくても構いません。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_xmas_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0307_season_xmas_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生が隣にいてくださるだけで十分ですから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0307_season_xmas_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH0307_Title",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ブルー、アーカイブ。うふふっ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%AE%A4%E7%AC%A0%20%E8%8C%9C/%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D/jp/CH0307_Title.ogg"
    }
  ],
  "voice_cn": [],
  "voice_kr": [],
